@page "/volunteer"
<PageTitle>Volunteer</PageTitle>

<h1 class="header-text">Become a Volunteer</h1>

<p class="intro-text">We are grateful for your willingness to help! Join our community and assist with temple activities. Your participation brings peace and harmony to those in need.</p>

<div class="volunteer-section">
    <h2>How You Can Help</h2>
    <p>There are many ways you can get involved—whether it’s helping with temple events, supporting our initiatives, or assisting with daily temple tasks. We appreciate any contribution you can make.</p>
</div>

<div class="volunteer-action">
    <h2>Ready to Make a Difference?</h2>
    <p>We're excited to have you on board! Fill out the form below or contact us to get started on your volunteer journey with us.</p>
    <a href="/CreateAccount" class="cta-button">Get in Touch</a>
</div>

<style>
    .header-text {
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 2em;
        color: #556b2f; /* Olive green */
        font-family: 'Georgia', 'Times New Roman', serif;
        margin: 50px 0 20px;
    }

    .intro-text {
        text-align: center;
        margin: 20px auto;
        max-width: 600px;
    }

    .volunteer-section, .volunteer-action {
        margin: 40px auto;
        max-width: 800px;
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0px 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); /* subtle shadow */
    }

    .volunteer-section h2, .volunteer-action h2 {
        font-size: 1.8em;
        color: #4f7c5d;
    }

    .volunteer-section p, .volunteer-action p {
        font-size: 1.1em;
        color: #333;
    }

    .cta-button {
        display: inline-block;
        background-color: #4f7c5d;
        color: white;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
        margin-top: 10px;
        font-weight: bold;
    }

    .cta-button:hover {
        background-color: #3e654a;
    }
</style>
